## 1. DEVICE IDENTIFICATION:
id: esp32-2432s028r
name: "ESP32-2432S028R (CYD - Cheap Yellow Display)"
manufacturer: Sunton
mcu: "ESP32-WROOM-32 dual-core LX6 up to 240 MHz; 4MB Flash; 520KB SRAM; Wi-Fi 802.11 b/g/n; BLE 4.2; 2.8in 320x240 ILI9341 TFT; XPT2046 resistive touch; microSD; RGB LED; LDR; speaker; CH340C USB-serial"
category: maker
image: esp32-2432s028r.svg
url: "https://github.com/witnessmenow/ESP32-Cheap-Yellow-Display"

## 2. TECH SPECS & DIMENSIONS:
specs: flashtotal 4194304 | flashavailable 4194304 | sram 540672 | eeprom 0 | clock 240000000 | voltage "3.3V" | cores 2 | wifi "802.11 b/g/n" | bluetooth "BLE 4.2"
dims: w 85.0 | h 50.0 | t 14.0

